    • BankAccount

      public BankAccount(String id, User[] users, String[] userId, Expense[] expenses, Income[] income, float total, Date createdAt, Date updatedAt, String currency, String ownerName)
      Constructor for the BankAccount class. Initializes a new instance of a bank account with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      id - The unique identifier of the bank account.
      users - An array of User objects associated with the bank account.
      userId - An array of user IDs linked to the bank account.
      expenses - An array of Expense objects associated with the bank account.
      income - An array of Income objects associated with the bank account.
      total - The total balance in the bank account.
      createdAt - The date when the bank account was created.
      updatedAt - The date when the bank account was last updated.
      currency - The currency used in the bank account.
      ownerName - The name of the owner of the bank account.
